data.name: Label6.Text
data.value: Alexander the Great Hotel, located in the heart of Alexandria, Egypt, offers 3-star accommodations with convenient amenities and a central location. The hotel is near major attractions, such as the Library of Alexandria (15 minutes away by car) and the Corniche waterfront promenade (5 minutes away). It features air-conditioned rooms with private balconies, free Wi-Fi, satellite TV, and minibars. Guests can enjoy a daily breakfast buffet and local cuisine at the on-site à la carte restaurant.
